        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "刘义庆，南北朝，学家，《世说新语》是由他组织批编写的。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1483272873841193,
          0.41043180846515603,
          0.7085852478839177,
